{"title":"轻装上路","authors":["鲍林"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":12,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻装上路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗地　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲍林　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，弹出了“1988”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号令枪还在庄严地冒烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用说，脚下不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天河运动场绛红色跑道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用说，山高、路险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目标——改革！一往无前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把因循守旧、妄自菲薄、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无所作为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远抛在后边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}